title: Luxusni Vegetarianska Restaurace at Eukalyptus
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, Organic, Raw, Salad bar, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Delivery, Take-out
description: A vegetarian coffee shop/restaurant offers vegan and raw meals. Prepares all meals with quality ingredients and uses no preservatives or additives. Also has a food shop. Try the alkaline coffee with reishi. You can enjoy coffees without caffeine, Ayurvedic coffee and spelt coffee. Other drinks include green young barley, acai, goji. Every visitor is served highly clear shungit water. Eukalyptus is a house of health and human development offering counseling, seminars, workshops in topic of holistic health, nutrition, ecology. Non-smoking. Wi-fi.
